description.en: Saren(https://saren.io/) is the governance token for our decentralized cryptocurrency tracker  app called "Cerberus" (https://cerberus.saren.io/). Which is currently already working and is still in further development. Holders of $SAR are currently able to vote on what tokens that may be listed on Cerberus and we have plans in the future for commenting, upvoting comments, creating proposals and staking regarding  the Cerberus app and other future apps created by the SAREN team.
